    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Пишем Spoiler-plugin для Octopress]]></title>
    <link href="http://ggoha.github.io/blog/2016/12/06/pishiem-spoiler-plugin-dlia-octopress/"/>
    <updated>2016-12-06T18:08:30+03:00</updated>
    <id>http://ggoha.github.io/blog/2016/12/06/pishiem-spoiler-plugin-dlia-octopress</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Мне изначально хотелось скрывать некоторые части постов под спойлер, например вот так
<img src="/images/spoiler.png">
Я смог найти только вот <a href="https://github.com/seanhagen/octopress-spoiler-tag/blob/master/spoiler.rb">это</a>
Но меня это не устраивало, так как это был однострочный спойлер, например, для &ldquo;спойлеров&rdquo; в фильме. Я же хотел скрывать некоторую часть текста, например, описание исправлений ошибок, которые в большинстве случаев не имеет смысла показывать.
Поэтому я решил написать его сам. Кроме того, я решил не использовать js, а обойтись только HTML/CSS.</p>

<!-- more -->


<script async src="//jsfiddle.net/hephunLe/16/embed/"></script>


<h2>CSS3</h2>

<p>Основная идея следующая
Переключатель представляет собой checkbox, для нажатого check с помощью селектора + (выбирающего следующие элементы) мы устанавливаем display:none для спойлерных объектов.
<div id='octopress-spoiler-tag'><input type='checkbox' id='octopress-spoiler-tag-7' class='octopress-spoiler-tag-head' checked/><label for='octopress-spoiler-tag-7'>Пояснение#1</label><div id='octopress-spoiler'>
  <figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>.octopress-spoiler-tag + label {
</span><span class='line'>      cursor: pointer;
</span><span class='line'>    }</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
  Позволяет изменять значение checkbox-a при нажатии на связанную с ним по id надпись.
</div></div></p>

<p><div id='octopress-spoiler-tag'><input type='checkbox' id='octopress-spoiler-tag-8' class='octopress-spoiler-tag-head' checked/><label for='octopress-spoiler-tag-8'>Пояснение#2</label><div id='octopress-spoiler'>
  <figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>.octopress-spoiler-tag:not(checked) {
</span><span class='line'>      position: absolute;
</span><span class='line'>      opacity: 0;
</span><span class='line'>    }</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
  Убирает с глаз долой дефолтный checkbox.
</div></div></p>

<h2>Ruby</h2>

<p>Основную структуру плагина я подсматривал у <a href="https://github.com/imathis/octopress/blob/master/plugins/blockquote.rb">blockquote</a>.
<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>spoiler.rb </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
<span class='line-number'>12</span>
<span class='line-number'>13</span>
<span class='line-number'>14</span>
<span class='line-number'>15</span>
<span class='line-number'>16</span>
<span class='line-number'>17</span>
<span class='line-number'>18</span>
<span class='line-number'>19</span>
<span class='line-number'>20</span>
<span class='line-number'>21</span>
<span class='line-number'>22</span>
<span class='line-number'>23</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='rb'><span class='line'><span class="k">module</span> <span class="nn">Jekyll</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="k">class</span> <span class="nc">Spoiler</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">lt</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="no">Liquid</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="no">Block</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="c1">#Зависит от того, хотим ли мы блок (многострочный как blockquote) или тег (однострочный как image)</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">initialize</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tag_name</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">text</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">tokens</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="c1">#собственно инициализация</span>
</span><span class='line'>      <span class="c1">#здесь нам делать особо нечего</span>
</span><span class='line'>      <span class="c1">#но возможно есть что инициализировать классу, что выше в цепочке наследования</span>
</span><span class='line'>      <span class="k">super</span>
</span><span class='line'>      <span class="vi">@text</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">text</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="k">end</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="sr">/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="sr">&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;def render(context)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="sr">#и вывод html</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="sr">  #получаем результат render-a предка</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="sr">  quote = super </span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="sr">  #оборачиваем в div, добавлем checkbox и label</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="sr">  &quot;&amp;lt;div id=&#39;octopress-spoiler-tag&#39;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;input type=&#39;checkbox&#39; id=&#39;octopress-spoiler-tag&#39; class=&#39;octopress-spoiler-tag-head&#39; checked/</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">gt</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">lt</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="n">label</span> <span class="k">for</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s1">&#39;octopress-spoiler-tag&#39;</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">gt</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="c1">#{@text}&amp;lt;/label&amp;gt;&amp;lt;div id=&#39;octopress-spoiler&#39;&amp;gt;&quot;+quote+&quot;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&quot;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="k">end</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="sr">/code&gt;&lt;/</span><span class="n">pre</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="nb">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>  <span class="k">end</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="k">end</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="no">Liquid</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="no">Template</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">register_tag</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">lsquo</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="n">spoiler</span><span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">rsquo</span><span class="p">;,</span> <span class="no">Jekyll</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="no">Spoiler</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
<div id='octopress-spoiler-tag'><input type='checkbox' id='octopress-spoiler-tag-9' class='octopress-spoiler-tag-head' checked/><label for='octopress-spoiler-tag-9'>Для поддержки нескольких спойлеров</label><div id='octopress-spoiler'>
  Нам необходимо понимать к какому checkbox относится label, это можно сделать с использованием id. Для этого нужно каждому спойлеру присвоить свой уникальный номер. В этом нам помогут переменные класса.
  <figure class='code'><figcaption><span>spoiler.rb </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='rb'><span class='line'>    <span class="k">class</span> <span class="nc">Spoiler</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">lt</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="no">Liquid</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="no">Block</span>
</span><span class='line'>      <span class="vc">@@sasa</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">hellip</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span><span class='line'>      <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">render</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">context</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'>        <span class="n">quote</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="k">super</span>
</span><span class='line'>        <span class="vc">@@sasa</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="vc">@@sasa</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
</span><span class='line'>        <span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">ldquo</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">div</span> <span class="nb">id</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s1">&#39;octopress-spoiler-tag&#39;</span><span class="o">&gt;&lt;</span><span class="n">input</span> <span class="n">type</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s1">&#39;checkbox&#39;</span> <span class="nb">id</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s1">&#39;octopress-spoiler-tag-#{@@sasa}&#39;</span> <span class="n">class</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s1">&#39;octopress-spoiler-tag-head&#39;</span> <span class="n">checked</span><span class="o">/&gt;&lt;</span><span class="n">label</span> <span class="k">for</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s1">&#39;octopress-spoiler-tag-#{@@sasa}&#39;</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="c1">#{@text}&lt;/label&gt;&lt;div id=&#39;octopress-spoiler&#39;&gt;&amp;rdquo;+quote+&amp;ldquo;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&amp;rdquo;</span>
</span><span class='line'>      <span class="k">end</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="p">}</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
  При каждом новом рендере, номер в id будет увеличиваться, что нам и необходимо.
</div></div></p>

